        <p>This apple pie recipe has been in my family for generation and never fails to delight. </p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>Ingredients</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>1/2 cup sugar</li>
            <li>2 tsp ground cinnamon</li>
            <li>6 medium-sized apples, peeled and sliced</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>Instructions</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Preheat oven to 375&deg;F (190&deg;C) </li>
            <li>In a bowl, mix the sugar and cinnamon.</li>
            <li>Toss the apples in the sugar-cinnamon mixture.</li>
        </ol>
